            <div class="faq-card c6"><h3>Do I need to train my voice before using it?</h3><p>No. SpeechRecognition.cloud uses AI-powered speech recognition that works immediately without any voice profile training. You install it and start dictating.</p></div>
            <div class="faq-card c6"><h3>What is the difference between the editions?</h3><p>Starter is free with 20 minutes per month. Personal/Educational adds unlimited usage and custom vocabulary at $119 AUD inc GST per year. Professional adds AI voice commands and advanced features at $239 AUD inc GST per year. Medical Ultra is the healthcare edition with medical vocabulary at $659 AUD inc GST per year.</p></div>
            <div class="faq-card c6"><h3>Does it work with my EMR or practice management system?</h3><p>Yes. Because it dictates directly at the cursor into any Windows application, it works with any software that accepts typed text input - including healthcare practice management systems, EMRs, and clinical documentation tools.</p></div>
            <div class="faq-card c6"><h3>How does it compare to Dragon for medical use?</h3><p>For ambient AI consultation capture and structured clinical note generation, Dragon Medical One is the more comprehensive solution. SpeechRecognition.cloud Medical Ultra suits clinicians who want straightforward Windows dictation with medical vocabulary at a lower price point.</p></div>
